snippet.textDisplay:
Why are some people who go outside don't wear masks? If masks are sold out, then improvise and be creative and have an initiative and make one out of clean and washable cloth, for at least the nose and mouth will be covered rather than letting it be more exposed. The virus when released by someone through sneezes and coughs can still stay alive on materials and the surrounding for half an hour or a bit more. So then, never remoce the mask or mouth and nose cover outdoors. Use masks and handle masks properly. Dispose medical masks or rewash fabric masks properly. Just always wash your hands for at least 20 seconds before and after doing something or going somewhere even inside in the house. Eat more fruits and vegetables. Observe social distancing with other persons for at least a meter or three feet even indoors or in one's home. Avoid bodily contact from others. Avoid going outside as much as possible, and to roam around, travel, or move around even in your community as much as possible. Always use alcohols or habd sanitizers, but proper hand washing is still the priority. Eat green, leafy, and bright fruits and vegetables. Take vitamins and food supplements to boost immune system. Exercise indoors or do household chores and cleaning or organizng everyday or thrice a week. When someone got colds, dry coughs, fever, difficulty in breathing, and muscle pain or any one of these, then immediately go safely to the nearest hospital and be treated, be interviwed of travel history and other stuffs, ask for testing for potentially having the virus, and then observe isolation and quarantine. At least this is how other countries try to deal with this virus.

We can all surpass this. I hope and pray that we all will.

Non mangiano cibi scarsamente digeriti: hot dog, hamburger, cioccolatini, biscotti, focacce dolci, torte, restano bloccati  nell'intestino, quando il coronovirus è infetto nel corpo, rimane più a lungo insieme al cibo bloccato e si verificano danni agli organi dei polmoni, allo stomaco e così via I virus vengono uccisi: aglio, cipolle rosse, ingoiano un po 'd'aglio, se qualcuno ha gastrite dello stomaco, beve latte caldo, altro  vitamina ,, c "mela, limousine  n, mandarini, noci di cocco. I prodotti rafforzano l'immunità: carne, porridge di grano saraceno, aglio, cipolle, rafano, vitamine, c "koumiss kazako, latte di cammello e sport.  Immunità agli spoiler: sigarette, droghe, cibi zuccherati, sporcizia umana, sudore congelato, sporcizia, prostituzione, AIDS, malattie a trasmissione sessuale.
